.SH NAME
vdu_controls \- vdu_controls 2.6.5rc4
.SH VDU_CONTROLS - A DDC CONTROL PANEL FOR MONITORS
.sp
A control panel for DisplayPort, DVI, HDMI, or USB\-connected VDUs (\fIVisual Display Units\fP).
